<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29610749-the-fiends-of-nightmaria"><img alt="The Fiends of Nightmaria  (The Tales of Bauchelain and Korbal Broach, #6)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1458825918l/29610749._SX98_.jpg" />
